message: Sorry, but Ozzy Osbourne's official Twitter also says September 20, 1980. I won't remove the American release date (no source) I'll just add one more source for September 20, 1980 using the vocalist's official twitter as a source, which I think is a reliable source.
There are no sources for the American release date. Only sources saying 20 September 1980. Loudwire and sources like an artist's official website are reliable sources.
